{"type": "article", "id": 21414, "title": "贝壳瓷器", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-28T07:32:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061414168lgeOioZEkb1CyGK.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利设计师 antonio aricò 创作了一组带有贝壳纹路的瓷器，餐盘、碗和勺柄上都有贝壳的螺旋纹，有凹凸的手感，在光的照射下也浮现出晶莹而有层次感的光泽。瓷器上的贝壳纹路还有粗糙的感觉，也有一种手工的质感。脆弱和奇特也兼具其中，让这套瓷器略有巴洛克的气质。<a href=\"http://www.antonioarico.com/index.php?/things/australian-shells--rmit-university-/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509396pn1h7JFi30qGIsL.jpg\" width=\"1052\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66539924\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150940ucStjws65WflRGFT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66539924\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615094038uaFme7xX04z6Ht.jpg\" width=\"1052\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66539924\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150941g3nbmJ7kaV8DWXY6.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50537634\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}